# GitWatcher - Environment Variables Example

# ─── Database Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────
# MongoDB Atlas connection URI string
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster.mongodb.net/gitwatcher?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# ─── Authentication ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# A secure, random 32+ character secret key for JWT session signing
# Generate one using: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_here

# ─── AI Service Integration ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini API key used for repository vulnerability scans and personas
# Obtain one from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ─── Optional GitHub Token ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional personal access token (PAT) to increase GitHub API rate limits from 60 to 5,000 requests/hour
# Obtain one from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token_here
